1
00:00:13,119 --> 00:00:14,240
Quite impressive, aren't you?

2
00:00:16,359 --> 00:00:17,960
The great master of Premier Medical Hall

3
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:22,079
using a little bastard for a disappearing act.

4
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,600
Truly eye-opening.

5
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:28,839
I was worried you'd pass secret messages

6
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,719
to lure your son here.

7
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,119
Little Stone is just a mountain boy.

8
00:00:34,399 --> 00:00:35,280
This has nothing to do with him.

9
00:00:35,719 --> 00:00:36,560
Let him go.

10
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,719
I'll do whatever you want.

11
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:40,719
Fine.

12
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,560
Time is running out.

13
00:00:44,119 --> 00:00:45,600
The last ingredient has been found.

14
00:00:46,079 --> 00:00:47,719
Now hurry up and make the medicine.

15
00:00:51,039 --> 00:00:52,520
Boss, what about this little bastard?

16
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,520
Who are you calling a bastard?

17
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,560
You're the bastard!

18
00:00:55,399 --> 00:00:55,840
Stop!

19
00:00:57,119 --> 00:00:58,600
Let him go and I'll agree to anything.

20
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:05,920
Little Stone, be good.

21
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,519
Go home now.

22
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,079
Live a good life.

23
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:13,799
Don't forget, you'll be a great hero.

24
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,480
I'm already grown up.

25
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,799
Master Ren, don't be afraid.

26
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,200
The great hero will come save us.

27
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,719
You silly child.

28
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,120
Still talking nonsense.

29
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:24,200
Keep talking nonsense and I'll get mad.

30
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,239
Get lost! Stop bothering me!

31
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:32,159
What are you doing? Let go of me!

32
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:34,959
Don't move.

33
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,200
Master Ren!

34
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,280
My patience has its limits.

35
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,599
Let go!

36
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,439
Watch the kid!

37
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,480
Stop right there!

38
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,400
You little brat!

39
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,799
Boss, someone's coming up the mountain.

40
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:14,719
How could he...

41
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,560
Well, well.

42
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,280
What a classic diversion.

43
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,800
You actually lured him here.

44
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,439
Perfect.

45
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,599
Time to end this.

46
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,199
Take him away, now.

47
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:44,560
Dad.

48
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,080
Uncle Ren.

49
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,680
Feifan.

50
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,639
Uncle Ren.

51
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,879
Stay back!

52
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,199
Don't come any closer!

53
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,439
Don't come any closer!

54
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:11,680
Don't come any closer!

55
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:18,840
Go!

56
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:21,759
Hurry!

57
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:22,560
Get out of here!

58
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,280
Dad.

59
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,520
Ranran.

60
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,919
I thought I'd never see you again.

61
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,319
Silly girl.

62
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,800
Daddy promised you.

63
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,039
I'd see you walk down the aisle.

64
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,039
Dad.

65
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:14,639
Dad.

66
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,920
It's all my fault.

67
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,920
I discovered the truth too late.

68
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,519
That's why for these four years, you...

69
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,600
Get up, quickly.

70
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,639
Don't say such silly things.

71
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,600
The one who imprisoned me

72
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:33,000
wasn't you.

73
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:36,319
Dad, Dad, what's wrong?

74
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,120
It's nothing, just an old ailment.

75
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,600
I heard

76
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,639
you've run Premier Medical Hall very well.

77
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,480
That useless fool

78
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,360
had this trick up his sleeve,

79
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:11,160
but ended up trapping himself first.

80
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:13,720
Come on, Dad, what's the rush?

81
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,920
Even if Ren Feifan finds something,

82
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,000
I won't let him succeed.

83
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:22,879
I have his weak spot right in my hands.

84
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,000
Come, try this tea.

85
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,240
Do you remember?

86
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:37,240
You broke this when you were seven.

87
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,720
Then do you still remember

88
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,600
when I secretly ate aconite at seven?

89
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,600
How could I forget?

90
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,839
You threw up until you turned blue,

91
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:50,000
clung to my neck crying, "Dad, save me,

92
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,560
am I going to die?"

93
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,240
What are you chatting about without me?

94
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,759
Feifan, come sit.

95
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:58,879
Dad.

96
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,240
Freshly picked osmanthus. Try some.

97
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:02,319
Alright.

98
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:16,199
The filling still has too much osmanthus.

99
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,920
Exactly like your mom used to make it.

100
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:27,199
If your mom could see you both now,

101
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,839
she'd surely be nagging again.

102
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,560
"Fang Hai,

103
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:35,720
look how well Feifan runs the hall.

104
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:40,439
Ran'er's acupuncture almost rivals mine."

105
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:49,519
She always said she'd give you the best.

106
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,079
Right now,

107
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,800
she must be so proud.

108
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,399
Well, well, Young Master Gu.

109
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:31,920
Is this...

110
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,759
a pink sports car?

111
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,600
After all these years,

112
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,120
you're as flashy as ever.

113
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,279
Don't even mention it.

114
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,879
I was going to give it to my girlfriend.

115
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:43,959
But before I could hand it over,

116
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,120
she cheated on me.

117
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,360
It's yours now.

118
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,680
No need for that.

119
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,439
Just fill in the amount yourself.

120
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,480
Are you crazy?

121
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:05,519
Four years apart,

122
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:10,160
and Doctor Ren still looks impressive.

123
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,319
What are you fumbling for?

124
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,519
Out with it.

125
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,959
What brings you back here?

126
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,959
Boss Ren,

127
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:19,800
the moment I heard you were out,

128
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,439
I rushed straight back to the country.

129
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,680
Still, I was a step too late.

130
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,319
Not too late.

131
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:28,120
I already know what the Wangs are after,

132
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,560
and I've gathered plenty of evidence.

133
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,279
Once sorted, I'll hand them to the police.

134
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,039
So you're out to bankrupt the Wangs.

135
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,440
You and your smart mouth.

136
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,919
Bring all evidence to swap in the suburbs.

137
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,240
No calling the police.

138
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,440
No bringing anyone along.

139
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,480
Is it that punk Wang Wenhao?

140
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,720
Here's the plan, Gu Yuan.

141
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,759
Get my family from Premier Medical Hall.

142
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,679
Take them to the safe house.

143
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:58,840
Got it.

144
00:08:59,320 --> 00:08:59,960
I'll send people to pick them up.

145
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,480
I'll go with you to save Young Lady Xu.

146
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,799
Listen to me, you go on your own.

147
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:04,840
I can't trust anyone else.

148
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:23,000
Brother Wenhao, please untie me, okay?

149
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,519
I'm begging you.

150
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:27,320
Let me go, Brother Wenhao.

151
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:32,679
Brother Wenhao.

152
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:35,720
Do you still remember?

153
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:36,879
When we were kids...

154
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,399
We used to go hiking together.

155
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:42,639
Once I fell and twisted my ankle.

156
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:46,080
You brought me to Premier Medical Hall.

157
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,279
To find Uncle Ren.

158
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,200
Do you remember?

159
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,919
Young Lady Xu.

160
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,720
What kind of act is this now?

161
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:03,519
Playing the tragic card, are we?

162
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,000
Brother Wenhao.

163
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,639
You can't keep making the same mistakes.

164
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,200
Young Lady Xu.

165
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,759
Right and wrong...

166
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,840
I decide that.

167
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:25,519
The Wangs set the rules in North City.

168
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:32,399
You can't bear the Wangs' sins alone.

169
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,799
Turn yourself in now.

170
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,120
Turn yourself in now.

171
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,480
There's still time to fix this.

172
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,159
Turn myself in?

173
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:46,480
Pray Ren Feifan's death isn't too brutal.

174
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:52,559
I bet you won't find him in one piece.

175
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,600
Let me go!

176
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,120
Let me go!

177
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,200
Wang Wenhao.

178
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,480
I'm just a weak girl.

179
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,399
You tied me up here.

180
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:12,960
Afraid I'd sprout wings and fly away?

181
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,720
Are you that afraid of Ren Feifan?

182
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,279
What?

183
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,399
Say that again.

184
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,159
I said...

185
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:31,519
I said, are you that afraid of Ren Feifan?

186
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:32,399
Me?

187
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:42,039
Young Mr. Wang.

188
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:45,559
Angry? Guess I hit the nail on the head.

189
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,519
I love seeing you angry.

190
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:52,000
I love seeing you angry.

191
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,440
Laugh.

192
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:56,840
Laugh.

193
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,840
Keep laughing.

194
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,200
When Ren Feifan dies...

195
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,720
You'll be laughing just like this.

196
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,679
Laugh!

197
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:14,679
Laugh!

198
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:25,080
Feifan!

199
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,720
Feifan, don't!

200
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:27,559
Stay back!

201
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:27,960
Ruojin.

202
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:29,639
Don't come any closer!

203
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,039
Ren Feifan

204
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:04,279
Let's have a little contest today.

205
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:07,440
See whether your fists are faster,

206
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:10,080
or my gun is faster.
